Enemies.

Either you say the truth to your investors, that this is going to take longer time than expected and there isn't that much profit you can expect in short term.

Or, you lie and hype up stocks.

So, the more you use AI tech, the higher benefit it is to use AI to replace AI. The only sound economic strategy is to replace a bad and expensive version of AI tech with a better and cheaper version.

Which means, you can't make money from AI, paradoxically.
